mb la normativa de desenvolupament, li garantim la seguretat i confidencialitat de les dades personals que ha facilitat. (Veure Política de privadesa).&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Els llocs de Wecorp poden incloure fòrums no moderats que contenen les opinions personals i altres expressions de les persones que publiquen entrades en una àmplia gamma de temes. Ni el contingut d&#039;aquest lloc ni els enllaços a altres llocs web es considera que hagin estat revisats ni aprovats per XXXX o qualsevol entitat afiliada a XXXX.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXX no és un editor de qualsevol dels continguts dels llocs, o de qualsevol contingut que pugui estar disponible a través d&#039;enllaços des de i cap a aquests, i actua exclusivament com un proveïdor de serveis d&#039;Internet. (Llei 34/2002, d&#039;11 de juliol LSSICI).&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Els textos i els materials en aquests llocs són l&#039;opinió del seu autor específic i no són declaracions de consell, opinió, o la informació de XXXX.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Si sent que podria ser ofès pel contingut dels llocs a través de Wecorp, no continuï.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;ALTRES&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXX no es fa responsable dels possibles errors de seguretat que es puguin produir, ni dels possibles danys que puguin causar-se al sistema informàtic de l&#039;usuari (maquinari i programari), els fitxers o documents emmagatzemats en aquest, com a conseqüència de la presència de virus a l&#039;ordinador de l&#039;usuari utilitzat per la connexió als serveis i continguts de Wecorp, d&#039;un mal funcionament del navegador o de l&#039;ús de versions no actualitzades d&#039;aquest.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;El lloc Wecorp pot contenir errors i omissions relatives a la descripció del producte, als preus i a la disponibilitat. Ens reservem el dret de corregir errors o omissions sense previ avís. També ens reservem el dret de cancel·lar qualsevol producte o servei ofert en el cas d&#039;error o omissió a la descripció, incloent preus, disponibilitat o per una altra raó.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;QUEIXES DEL COPYRIGHT&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXX respecta els drets de propietat intel·lectual d&#039;altres. Si creu que els seus drets d&#039;autor han estat violats en un lloc de Wecorp, informeu-nos-en immediatament a l&#039;adreça proporcionada en aquestes condicions.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;ARXIUS DE REGISTRE&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Igual que molts altres llocs web, Wecorp fa servir arxius de registre.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p style=&#034;line-height:normal;background:white;&#034;&gt;La informació continguda en aquests arxius inclou adreces de protocol d&#039;Internet (IP), tipus de navegador, proveïdor de serveis d&#039;Internet (ISP), data/hora, pàgines de referència/sortida, i el nombre de clics per analitzar tendències, administrar el moviment del lloc, rastrejar l&#039;usuari entorn del lloc i recopilar informació demogràfica. Adreces IP i altra informació que no està vinculada a cap informació que sigui personalment identificable.&lt;/p&gt;</value></preference><preference><name>portletSetupShowBorders</name><value>false</value></preference><preference><name>tr_TR_htmlcode</name><value>&lt;div class=&#034;scrollContent_box scrollContent_boxContador2&#034; id=&#034;scrollContent_boxContador2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong style=&#034;color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&#034;&gt;[EDITAR TEXTO AVISO LEGAL]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;div class=&#034;scrollContent_box scrollContent_boxContador2&#034; id=&#034;scrollContent_boxContador2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h2&gt;YASAL UYARI&lt;/h2&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/div&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wecorp © Telefónica Educación Digital (TED)&lt;/strong&gt;, S.L.U.&#039;nun mülküdür. Madrid, 2015.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Tüm hakları saklıdır.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;MÜLK SAHİBİ&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX, 11 Temmuz tarihli, 34/2002 sayılı, bilgi toplumu ve elektronik ticaret hizmetleri konulu yasaya uygun olarak sizi şu konuda bilgilendirir:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;ul&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;Şirketin adı XXXXX&#039;dur.&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;Vergi numarası XXXXX&#039;tür.&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;XXXXX, XXX. cildinin; XXX. defterinin, XX. kısmının, XXXXX. sayfasına kayıtlıdır.&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;Şirketin adresi XXXXX, XXXXX, XXXXX, XXXXX&#039;dir.&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;Bizimle iletişime geçmek için bize elektronik posta gönderebilirsiniz: XXXX@XXX.XX&amp;nbsp;ve şu numaradan arayabilirsiniz: +XXXXX. Müşteri hizmetleri, XXXXX&#039;den XXXXX, XXXX XX-XX arası hizmet sunmaktadır.&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/ul&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;FERAGATNAME&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;15/1999 Sayılı Kişisel Nitelikteki Verilerin Korunması Kanununa ve yönetmeliğine uygun olarak; tarafınızca sunulan kişisel verilerin güvenliğini ve gizliliğini garanti ediyoruz. (Gizlilik Politikasına bakınız).&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Wecorp sitelerinde, birçok konu hakkında kişisel fikirleri ve herkese açık yorumları içeren ve modere edilmemiş forumlar bulunabilir. Bu web sitesinin içeriği ve diğer sitelerin bağlantıları Telefónica Educación Digital ya da XXXX&#039;a bağlı başka herhangi bir birim tarafından revize edilmemiş ve onaylanmamıştır.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXX sitelerin herhangi bir içeriğinin ya da bu sitelerdeki bağlantılar aracılığıyla ulaşılabilecek olan herhangi bir içeriğin editörü değildir ve sadece bir İnternet hizmeti sağlayıcısı olarak işlev görmektedir. (11 Temmuz tarihli, 34/2002 sayılı BTETHK).&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Bu sitelerdeki metin ve materyaller, bunları yayınlayan kişinin fikridir ve XXXX&#039;in tavsiyesi, fikri ya da bilgisi değildir.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Eğer Wecorp aracılığıyla ulaştığınız sitelerin içeriği sizi rahatsız ediyorsa devam etmemelisiniz.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;DİĞER&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXX, Wecorp&#039;un hizmetlerine ve içeriklerine bağlanmak için kullanıcının kullandığı bilgisayarına bir virüs bulaşması, tarayıcının kötü işlemesi veya güncellenmemiş tarayıcı sürümlerinin kullanımı sonucu kullanıcının bilgi işlem sisteminde (donanım ve yazılım), bilgisayarda kayıtlı bulunan dosya ya da belgelerde meydana gelebilecek olan olası hasarlardan sorumlu tutulamaz.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Wecorp sitesi, ürün tanımı, ücret ve mevcudiyet ile ilişkili hata ve eksiklikler içerebilir. Önceden haber vermeden hata veya eksiklikleri düzeltme hakkına sahibiz. Aynı zamanda ücret, mevcudiyet veya herhangi başka bir neden dahil olmak üzere tanımda bir hata veya eksiklik olması halinde sunulan herhangi bir ürün veya hizmeti iptal etme hakkına da sahibiz.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;TELİF HAKKI ŞİKAYETLERİ&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXX, diğer kişilerin fikri mülkiyet haklarına saygı gösterir. Eğer bir Wecorp sitesinde fikri mülkiyet hakkınızın ihlal edildiğini düşünüyorsanız, lütfen en kısa zamanda bu koşullar için verilen adres aracılığıyla bizi bilgilendirin.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;KAYIT ARŞİVLERİ&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Birçok diğer Web sitesi gibi, Wecorp kayıt arşivlerini kullanmaktadır.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/div&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Bu arşivlerde yer alan bilgilere, eğilimleri analiz etmek, sitenin hareketini yönetmek, sitenin çevresindeki kullanıcının izini sürmek ve demografik bilgi toplamak amacıyla İnternet protokolü adresleri (IP), tarayıcı türü, İnternet hizmet sağlayıcısı (ISP), tarih / saat, referans / çıkış sayfaları ve tıklama sayısı dahildir. IP adresleri ve diğer bilgilerle ilişkili olmayan, kişisel olarak tanımlanabilir diğer bilgiler.&lt;/p&gt;</value></preference><preference><name>zh_CN_htmlcode</name><value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#034;font-size: 16px;&#034;&gt;&lt;span style=&#034;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&#034;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[EDITAR TEXTO AVISO LEGAL]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;div class=&#034;scrollContent_box scrollContent_boxContador2&#034; id=&#034;scrollContent_boxContador2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h2&gt;法律声明&lt;/h2&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/div&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wecorp版权所属西班牙电信数字教育(©TED)&lt;/strong&gt;公司马德里 2015&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;保留所有权利。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;所有权&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;西班牙电信数字教育公司，根据7月11日关于信息和电子商务服务公司的第34/2002号法律，声明：&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;ul&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;公司名为西班牙电信数字教育公司。&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;税号为B/82.857.053。&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;登记于马德里工商局卷17.963; 簿 0; 章节 8ª; 页 M-268.715。&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;其注册地址位于格兰大道28号，马德里2803。&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;与我们取得联系，可通过电子邮件：&lt;a href=&#034;mailto:protecciondedatos.tls@telefonica.com&#034;&gt;protecciondedatos.tls@telefonica.com&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;或通过电话 +34 91 4830108.开放时间周一至周五西班牙半岛时间8点到19点。&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/ul&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;免责声明&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;根据“组织法”第15/1999号“个人信息保护法”（LOPD）条例规定，我们保证您所提供的个人资料的安全性和保密性。（见隐私政策）。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Wecorp网站可包括非未经审查论坛，其中发表个人意见及其它言论涵盖广泛的话题。本网站的内容以及连接到其它网站的链接未经西班牙电信数字教育公司及其相关机构的审核或批准。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;西班牙电信数字教育公司不是网站的内容，或任何链接内容的编辑，仅作为互联网服务供应商。（LSSICI 7月11日第34/2002号法律）。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;这些网站上的文本和材料反映其作者的意见，不是西班牙电信数字教育公司的建议，意见或言论。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;如果您觉得Wecorp网站可能含有冒犯内容，那么请不要继续浏览。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;其它&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;西班牙电信数字教育公司不对可能的安全错误或任何可能导致用户计算机系统（硬件和软件），存储在其中的文件或文档，已存在的用于连接Wecorp服务和内容的病毒，浏览器的故障或使用未更新版本而造成的病毒带来的任何损害承担责任。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Wecorp网站可能包含与产品，价格及可用性信息有关的错误或遗漏。我们保留更正错误或遗漏的权利，恕不另行通知。我们保留当信息出现错误或遗漏时，因定价，可用性或任何其它原因，取消提供产品或服务的权利。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;版权投诉&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;西班牙电信数字教育公司尊重他人的知识产权。如果您认为您的版权收到Wecorp网站的侵犯，请在以下这些情况下立即通过所提供的地址通知我们。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;注册文件&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;与大多数其它网站一样，Wecorp使用注册文件。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;在这些文件中所含的信息包括互联网协议地址（IP），浏览器类型，互联网服务提供商（ISP），日期/时间，参考页面/退出页面以及点击次数，用于趋势分析，管理站点活动， 在站点上追踪用户并收集人口统计信息。IP地址和其它与个人身份信息无关的信息。&lt;/p&gt;</value></preference></portlet-preferences>'),
	(12683, 0, 3, 10507, 'htmlcontent_WAR_weCorpportlet_INSTANCE_0aTUuuAzfxS4', '<portlet-preferences><preference><name>en_US_htmlcode</name><value>&lt;h1 style=&#034;margin-top:15.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm;&#034;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&#034;background:white;font-weight:normal;&#034;&gt;&lt;span style=&#034;color:red;&#034;&gt;&lt;span style=&#034;font-family:source,serif;&#034;&gt;&lt;span style=&#034;font-size:12.0pt;&#034;&gt;[EDITAR TEXTO POLÍTICA DE COOKIES]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h1&gt;Cookies Policy&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX informs Users, via this notice, that cookies may be used when the User browses different section of the Website. While using the Website, the User expressly accepts and authorizes the use of cookies.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;What are cookies?&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;A cookie is a data file that is generated in your computer when you access certain web pages to store and recover browsing information that occurs from said computer. For more information about cookies, XXXXX invites you to click on the following link:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#034;http://www.iabspain.net/privacidadeninternet/&#034;&gt;http://www.iabspain.net/privacidadeninternet/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;This document intends to help the XXXXX Website User to understand the different security levels associated with the cookies used on our Website, as well as under what circumstances we request the User&#039;s prior permission, as a condition prior to storage. As an additional guarantee to those described above, the User&#039;s registration in the SIELE Account is subject to the User accepting cookies during the installation or update of the employed browser, and this acceptance may be revoked at any time via the available content and privacy configuration options.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are cookies for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;The purpose of cookies use is to remember User preferences (language, country, session log-in, browser characteristics, information regarding use of our Website, etc.) as well as, among others, to measure audience and traffic values, and to control the progress and number of User entries.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;By remembering User preferences, we can know the characteristics of the computer being used and are therefore able to offer a better browsing experience. Cookies can help our Website to distinguish a User&#039;s browser as a previous visitor and thereby store and remember the previously established preferences while the User was browsing the Website, personalize the start page, identify which sections of a site have been visited, or maintain a list of selected items in a &#034;shopping cart&#034;.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX may use cookies with the aim of recognizing Users that have registered and therefore be able to offer them an improved and more personalized service.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Likewise, these may be used to gather information regarding the date and time of the User&#039;s last visit, to measure traffic values within the Website itself, and to estimate the number of visits made, in such a way that XXXXX can more effectively focus and adapt its Services.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Websites normally use cookies to obtain statistical information about their web pages. The User must keep in mind that we collect data on User movement and Website use as statistical data, not personal data.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cookie types and uses&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Below is a list of the cookies that you may find on our Website and a brief description of their purposes. Some cookies personalize your visit and others remember your preferences, while others only provides us with visitor statistics.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personalized cookies&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;What are they for?&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Personalization cookies enable information to be stored regarding preferences, User language, browser type used for access, etc. with the purpose of displaying content and offers of particular interest to the User and to register the number of times that XXXXX displays a specific message (new features of the Website, generally).&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Notice regarding the deletion of personalization cookies:&amp;nbsp;XXXXX informs the User that if the User deletes personalization cookies, he or she will have to update their preferences every time they begin a session on the Website or, if using a different device, computer profile, or browser, they will have to newly communicate their preferences to XXXXX. Similarly, this may prevent the proper functioning of some functions.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;Technical cookies&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;These cookies allow the User to browse our Website and to use the different options and services it presents. Thus, it allows the User:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;ul&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;To identify the session&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;To access sections with restricted access&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;To remember elements in the shopping cart&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;To make purchases&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;To request registration or to participate in an event&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/ul&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Third party technical cookies&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX uses Google Maps to view geographic locations. This use implies the remission of cookies (PREF and NID) entirely managed by Google.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;First or third party Cookies Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;What are they for?&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;This type of cookie, either dealt with by XXXXX or third parties, provides statistical information about User&#039;s use of the Website, for example, what sections are visited, if there have been technical problems when accessing said sections, etc. These cookies do not allow the User to be identified, given that the information collected is anonymous and will be used solely to work on improving the Website design and browsing of the same, use statistics, search speeds, measurement of Website activity, etc.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Third party cookies to manage advertising space&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;What are they for?&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;These are cookies that are stored by third party companies that manage the spaces for XXXXX advertising and those that Users access. These cookies enable us to measure online campaign effectiveness, provide information of interest, and offer preferred marketing content for Users.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;table border=&#034;1&#034; cellpadding=&#034;0&#034; cellspacing=&#034;0&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Cookies&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Information (*)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Purpose&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;4&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;OWN COOKIES&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Strictly necessary&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Session, register, data to distinguish free services from paid services&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Registration management&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Provide information society services requested by the User and in accordance with the applicable terms and conditions&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;4&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;THIRD PARTY COOKIES&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;(the following collected information has been provided by those third parties)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Analíticas&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Google Analytics&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Number of visits, pages or sections visited, browsing time, sites visited before entering this page, details on the browsers used.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Statistical reports on Website traffic, total audience and audience for a specific marketing campaign.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Comscore&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Number of visits, pages or sections visited, browsing time, sites visited before entering this page, details on the browsers used.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Statistical reports on Website traffic, total audience and audience for a specific marketing campaign.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Score Card Research(Full Circle Studies, Inc.)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Browsing time, website visited and information related to own browsing&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Creates reports about general Website visit patterns.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;/tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/table&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;(*) Information obtained via these cookies, referred to the User&#039;s computer, may be combined with your personal data only if you are registered with the Website.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;Protective safeguards&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;The User may configure his or her browser to accept or not accept the cookies it receives, or to inform the User when a server wants to store a cookie to delete them from the computer. You can find these instructions in your browser&#039;s security configuration.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Examples:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;ul&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;If you use Microsoft Internet Explorer, in the menu option Tools&amp;gt; Internet Options &amp;gt; Privacy &amp;gt; Configuration (&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&#034;http://windows.microsoft.com/es-es/windows7/how-to-manage-cookies-in-internet-explorer-9&#034;&gt;http://windows.microsoft.com/es-es/windows7/how-to-manage-cookies-in-internet-explorer-9&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;If you use Firefox, in the menu option Tools&amp;gt; Options &amp;gt; Privacy &amp;gt; Cookies (&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&#034;http://support.mozilla.org/es/kb/habilitar-y-deshabilitar-cookies-que-los-sitios-we&#034;&gt;http://support.mozilla.org/es/kb/habilitar-y-deshabilitar-cookies-que-los-sitios-we&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;If you use Google Chrome, in the menu option Configuration &amp;gt; Privacy (&lt;a href=&#034;http://support.google.com/chrome/bin/answer.py?hl=es&amp;amp;answer=95647&#034;&gt;http://support.google.com/chrome/bin/answer.py?hl=es&amp;amp;answer=95647&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;If you use Safari, in the menu option Preferences &amp;gt; Security (&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&#034;http://support.apple.com/kb/ph5042&#034;&gt;http://support.apple.com/kb/ph5042&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/ul&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;The User may use the &#034;Help&#034; section, found in the tool bar of most browsers, to change their computer settings, however, some of the characteristics of our online services may not function properly or access to the same may be more difficult if your computer rejects all cookies.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Many browsers allow you to activate a privacy mode through which Cookies are always deleted after visiting a web page. Depending on the browser, this privacy mode may have different names. Below you can find a list of the most common browsers and the different names for this &#034;privacy mode&#034;:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;ul&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;Internet Explorer 8 and higher: InPrivate&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;Firefox 3.5 and higher: Private Browsing&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;Google Chrome 10 and higher: Incognito&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;Safari 2 and higher: Private Browsing&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;li&gt;Opera 10.5 and higher: Private Browsing&lt;/li&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/ul&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Please carefully read the help section in your browser to find out more about how to active the &#034;privacy mode.&#034; You can continue visiting our Website even if your browser is in &#034;privacy mode,&#034; however, the User experience may not be ideal and some functions may not work properly.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX thanks those Users who accept Cookies, as this helps us gather more precise data that allows us to improve the Content and design of our Website and to better adapt it to your preferences.&lt;/p&gt;</value></preference><preference><name>es_ES_htmlcode</name><value>&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong style=&#034;color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&#034;&gt;[EDITAR TEXTO POLÍTICA DE COOKIES]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h1&gt;Política de Cookies&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX comunica a los usuarios, a través de este aviso, que puede utilizar cookies cuando el usuario navega por las diferentes páginas del sitio. Durante el uso de nuestra página web aceptas y autorizas expresamente el uso de cookies, de acuerdo con nuestra política de privacidad.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;La utilización de las cookies tiene como finalidad exclusiva recordar las preferencias del usuario (idioma, país, inicio de sesión, características de su navegador, información de uso de nuestra Web, etc.)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Recordando sus preferencias sabremos las características del ordenador que está usando y así podremos ofrecerle una mejor experiencia de navegación. Las cookies pueden ayudar a nuestro sitio Web a distinguir el navegador del usuario como visitante anterior y así guardar y recordar las preferencias que puedan haberse establecido mientras el usuario estaba navegando por el sitio, personalizar las páginas de inicio, identificar qué sectores de un sitio han sido visitados o mantener un registro de selecciones en un &#034;carro de compra&#034;.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX puede utilizar las cookies con el objeto de reconocer a los usuarios que se hayan registrado y poder ofrecerles un mejor servicio y más personalizado.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Asimismo pueden ser utilizadas para obtener información acerca de la fecha y hora de la última visita del usuario, medir algunos parámetros de tráfico dentro del propio site y estimar el número de visitas realizadas, de manera que XXXXX pueda enfocar y ajustar los servicios de forma más efectiva.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Normalmente los sitios Web utilizan las cookies para obtener información estadística sobre sus páginas Web. Tenga en cuenta que recogemos datos sobre sus movimientos y uso de nuestra Web como datos estadísticos, no personales.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;Tipos y finalidades de las cookies&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;A continuación se presenta una lista de las cookies que puede encontrar en nuestro sitio Web y una breve descripción de su finalidad. Le aseguramos que ninguna de ellas conserva información de identificación personal sobre usted. Algunas cookies personalizan su visita, otras recuerdan sus preferencias, mientras que otras solo nos proveen estadísticas de los visitantes.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;table border=&#034;1&#034; cellpadding=&#034;0&#034; cellspacing=&#034;0&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;th&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Cookies&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/th&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;th&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Información (*)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/th&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;th&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Finalidad&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/th&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;4&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;COOKIES PROPIAS&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Estrictamente necesarias&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Sesión, registro, datos para distinguir los servicios gratuitos de los servicios de pago&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Gestión del registro&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Prestar servicios de la sociedad de la información solicitados por el usuario y conforme a los términos y condiciones aplicables&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;4&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;COOKIES DE TERCEROS&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;(la información recogida a continuación ha sido facilitada por esos terceros)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td rowspan=&#034;7&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Analíticas&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Google Analytics&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Número de visitas, páginas o secciones visitadas, tiempo de navegación, sitios visitados antes de entrar en esta página, detalles sobre los navegadores usados.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Informes estadísticos sobre el tráfico del sitio web, su audiencia total y la audiencia en una determinada campaña publicitaria.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Comscore&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Número de visitas, páginas o secciones visitadas, tiempo de navegación, sitios visitados antes de entrar en esta página, detalles sobre los navegadores usados.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Informes estadísticos sobre el tráfico del sitio web, su audiencia total y la audiencia en una determinada campaña publicitaria.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Score Card Research (Full Circle Studies, Inc.)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Tiempo de navegación, sitio web visitado e información relacionada con la propia navegación&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Crear informes sobre patrones generales de visitas al sitio web.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;/tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/table&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;(*) La información obtenida a través de estas cookies, referida al equipo del usuario, podrá ser combinada con sus datos personales solo si usted está registrado en este sitio web.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;Salvaguardias de protección&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;El usuario puede configurar su navegador para aceptar, o no, las cookies que recibe o para que el navegador le avise cuando un servidor quiera guardar una cookie o borrarlas de su ordenador. Puede encontrar las instrucciones en la configuración de seguridad en su navegador Web.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Ejemplos:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;· Si utiliza Microsoft Internet Explorer, en la opción de menú Herramientas &amp;gt; Opciones de Internet &amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&amp;nbsp; Privacidad &amp;gt; &amp;nbsp;Configuración.&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Si utiliza Firefox, en la opción de menú Herramientas &amp;gt; Opciones &amp;gt; Privacidad &amp;gt; Cookies.&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Si utiliza Google Chrome, en la opción de menú Configuración &amp;gt; Privacidad&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Si utiliza Safari, en la opción de menú Preferencias &amp;gt; Seguridad&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Puede hacer uso de la sección &#034;Ayuda&#034; que encontrará en la barra de herramientas de la mayoría de navegadores para cambiar los ajustes de su ordenador, sin embargo, algunas de las características de nuestros servicios online pueden no funcionar o pueden resultar más complicadas de acceder si rechaza todas las cookies.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Muchos navegadores permiten activar un modo privado mediante el cual las cookies se borran siempre después de su visita. Dependiendo de cada navegador, este modo privado puede tener diferentes nombres, abajo puede encontrar una lista de los navegadores más comunes y los diferentes nombres de este &#034;modo privado&#034;:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;· Internet Explorer 8 y superior: InPrivate&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· FireFox 3.5 y superior: Navegación Privada&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Google Chrome 10 y superior: Incógnito&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Safari 2 y superior: Navegación Privada&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Opera 10.5 y superior: Navegación Privada&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Por favor, lea atentamente la sección de ayuda de su navegador para conocer más acerca de como activar el &#034;modo privado&#034;. Podrá seguir visitando nuestra Web aunque su navegador esté en &#034;modo privado&#034;, no obstante, la experiencia de usuario puede no ser óptima y algunas utilidades pueden no funcionar.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX le agradece que active la aceptación de cookies, esto nos ayuda a obtener datos más precisos que nos permiten mejorar el contenido y el diseño de nuestra página Web para adaptarlo a sus preferencias.&lt;/p&gt;</value></preference><preference><name>it_IT_htmlcode</name><value>&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong style=&#034;color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&#034;&gt;[EDITAR TEXTO POLÍTICA DE COOKIES]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h1&gt;Politica dei Cookie&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Con il presente avviso XXXXX informa gli utenti che può utilizzare alcuni cookie durante la navigazione nelle pagine del sito web. In conformità della nostra politica sulla privacy l&#039;utente accetta e autorizza espressamente l&#039;uso dei cookie durante la visita della nostra pagina web.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;L&#039;utilizzo dei cookie ha come unico fine di memorizzare le preferenze dell&#039;utente (lingua, paese, accesso, caratteristiche del browser, informazioni sull&#039;uso della nostra Web, ecc.).&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Grazie alla memorizzazione delle preferenze dell&#039;utente è possibile conoscere le caratteristiche del computer che sta utilizzando e offrire un&#039;esperienza di navigazione migliore. I cookie possono aiutare il nostro sito Web a riconoscere il browser dell&#039;utente quale visitatore abituale e a salvare e memorizzare le preferenze impostatesi eventualmente durante la navigazione dell&#039;utente sul sito, a personalizzare le home page, a identificare i determinati settori visitati di un sito web o ad avere la traccia del contenuto selezionato nel &#034;cestino degli acquisti&#034;.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX può utilizzare i cookie con il fine di riconoscere gli utenti registrati e di offrire un servizio migliore e personalizzato.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;I cookie possono essere utilizzati anche per ottenere informazioni sulla data e l&#039;ora dell&#039;ultima visita dell&#039;utente, misurare alcuni parametri di traffico sul sito stesso e calcolare il numero delle visite effettuate per consentire a XXXXX di orientare e adattare i servizi in modo effettivo.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;In genere i siti Web utilizzano i cookie per ottenere dati statistici relativi all&#039;uso delle pagine Web. I dati sui movimenti e sull&#039;uso della nostra Web da parte degli utenti sono raccolti come dati statistici, non personali.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;Tipi e scopi dei cookie&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Di seguito si presenta un elenco dei cookie che si possono trovare sul nostro sito Web e una breve descrizione dello scopo per cui vengono utilizzati. Assicuriamo che nessun cookie conserva le informazioni personali dell&#039;utente. Alcuni cookie personalizzano la visita dell&#039;utente, altri memorizzano le preferenze, altri ancora forniscono dati statistici sui visitatori.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;table border=&#034;1&#034; cellpadding=&#034;0&#034; cellspacing=&#034;0&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cookie&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Informazioni (*)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scopo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;4&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;COOKIE PROPRI&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Strettamente necessari&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Sessione, registro, dati per distinguere i servizi gratuiti da quelli a pagamento&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Gestione del registro&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Fornire i servizi della società delle informazioni richiesti dall&#039;utente e in conformità dei termini e delle condizioni applicabili&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td style=&#034;border:none;border-right:inset 1.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;&#034;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;4&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;CO