ody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/table&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;(*) A informação obtida através destes cookies, referente ao equipamento do usuário, poderá ser combinada com seus dados pessoais somente se você estiver registrado neste website.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;Garantias de proteção&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;O usuário pode configurar seu navegador para aceitar, ou não, as cookies que recebe ou para que o navegador avise quando um servidor quiser guardar uma cookie ou excluí-las do seu computador. As instruções podem ser encontradas na configuração de segurança do seu navegador web.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Exemplos:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;· Se utilizar Microsoft Internet Explorer, na opção de menu Ferramentas&amp;gt; Opções de Internet &amp;gt; Privacidade &amp;gt; Configuração.&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Se utilizar Firefox, na opção do menu Ferramentas&amp;gt; Opções &amp;gt; Privacidade &amp;gt; Cookies.&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Se utilizar Google Chrome, na opção de menu Configuração &amp;gt; Privacidade&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Se utilizar Safari, na opção de menu Preferências &amp;gt; Segurança&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Pode utilizar a seção “Ajuda”, na barra de ferramentas da maioria de navegadores, para mudar os ajustes do seu computador; no entanto, algumas das características de nossos serviços online podem não funcionar ou ficar menos acessíveis se você recusar todos as cookies.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Muitos navegadores permitem ativar um modo privado através do qual as cookies sempre são excluídas depois da sua visita. Dependendo de cada navegador, este modo privado pode ter diferentes nomes; veja abaixo uma lista dos navegadores mais comuns e os diferentes nomes deste “modo privativo”:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;· Internet Explorer 8 y superior: InPrivate&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· FireFox 3.5 y superior: Navegación Privada&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Google Chrome 10 y superior: Incógnito&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Safari 2 y superior: Navegación Privada&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Opera 10.5 y superior: Navegación Privada&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Por favor, leia atentamente a seção de ajuda de seu navegador para saber mais sobre como ativar o “modo privativo”. Você poderá continuar visitando nosso Site mesmo que seu navegador esteja em “modo privativo”; não obstante, a experiência de usuário pode não ser perfeita e algumas utilidades podem não funcionar.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX agradece que você ative a aceitação das cookies; isto nos ajuda a obter dados mais precisos que nos permitem melhorar o conteúdo e o design de nosso Site para adaptá-lo as suas preferências.&lt;/p&gt;</value></preference><preference><name>ca_ES_htmlcode</name><value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&#034;background:white;font-weight:normal;&#034;&gt;&lt;span style=&#034;color:red;&#034;&gt;&lt;span style=&#034;font-family:source,serif;&#034;&gt;&lt;span style=&#034;font-size:12.0pt;&#034;&gt;[EDITAR TEXTO POLÍTICA DE COOKIES]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h1&gt;Política de galetes&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX comunica als usuaris, mitjançant aquest avís, que pot utilitzar galetes quan l&#039;usuari navega per les diferents pàgines del lloc. Durant l&#039;ús de la nostra pàgina web, accepta i autoritza expressament l&#039;ús de galetes, d&#039;acord amb la nostra política de privadesa.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;La utilització de les galetes té com a finalitat exclusiva recordar les preferències de l&#039;usuari (llengua, país, inici de sessió, característiques del seu navegador, informació d&#039;ús de la nostra web, etc.)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Recordant les seves preferències sabrem les característiques de l&#039;ordinador que està fent servir i així podrem oferir-li una millor experiència de navegació. Les galetes poden ajudar el nostre lloc web a distingir el navegador de l&#039;usuari com a visitant anterior i així guardar i recordar les preferències que puguin haver-se establert mentre l&#039;usuari estava navegant pel lloc, personalitzar les pàgines d&#039;inici, identificar quins sectors d&#039;un lloc han estat visitats o mantenir un registre de seleccions en un &#034;carro de compra&#034;.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX pot utilitzar les galetes amb l&#039;objectiu de reconèixer els usuaris que s&#039;hagin registrat i poder oferir-los un servei millor i més personalitzat.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Així mateix, poden ser utilitzades per obtenir informació sobre la data i l&#039;hora de l&#039;última visita de l&#039;usuari, mesurar alguns paràmetres de trànsit dins del propi site i estimar el nombre de visites realitzades, de manera que XXXXX pugui enfocar i ajustar els serveis de manera més efectiva.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Normalment els llocs web utilitzen les galetes per obtenir informació estadística sobre les seves pàgines web. Recordi que recollim dades sobre els seus moviments i ús de la nostra web com a dades estadístiques, no personals.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;Tipus i finalitats de les galetes&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;A continuació es presenta una llista de les galetes que pot trobar al nostre lloc web i una breu descripció de la seva finalitat. Li assegurem que cap d&#039;aquestes conserva informació d&#039;identificació personal sobre vostè. Algunes galetes personalitzen la seva visita, altres recorden les seves preferències, mentre que altres només ens proveeixen estadístiques dels visitants.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;table border=&#034;1&#034; cellpadding=&#034;0&#034; cellspacing=&#034;0&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Galetes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Informació (*)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Finalitat&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;4&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;GALETES PRÒPIES&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Estrictament necessàries&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Sessió, registre, dades per distingir els serveis gratuïts dels serveis de pagament&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Gestió del registre&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Prestar serveis de la societat de la informació sol·licitats per l&#039;usuari i d&#039;acord amb els termes i les condicions aplicables&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;4&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;GALETES DE TERCERS&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;(La informació recollida a continuació ha estat facilitada per aquests tercers)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td rowspan=&#034;7&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Analítiques&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td style=&#034;border:none;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;&#034;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td style=&#034;border:none;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;&#034;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Google Analytics&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Nombre de visites, pàgines o seccions visitades, temps de navegació, llocs visitats abans d&#039;entrar a aquesta pàgina, detalls sobre els navegadors utilitzats.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Informes estadístics sobre el trànsit del lloc web, la seva audiència total i l&#039;audiència en una determinada campanya publicitària.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Comscore&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Nombre de visites, pàgines o seccions visitades, temps de navegació, llocs visitats abans d&#039;entrar a aquesta pàgina, detalls sobre els navegadors utilitzats.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Informes estadístics sobre el trànsit del lloc web, la seva audiència total i l&#039;audiència en una determinada campanya publicitària.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Score Card Research (Full Circle Studies, Inc.)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Temps de navegació, lloc web visitat i informació relacionada amb la pròpia navegació&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Crear informes sobre patrons generals de visites al lloc web.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td style=&#034;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:inset 1.0pt;border-right:inset 1.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;&#034;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;/tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/table&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;(*) La informació obtinguda a través d&#039;aquestes galetes, referida a l&#039;equip de l&#039;usuari, podrà ser combinada amb les seves dades personals només si vostè està registrat en aquest lloc web.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;Salvaguardes de protecció&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;L&#039;usuari pot configurar el seu navegador per acceptar, o no, les galetes que rep o perquè el navegador l&#039;avisi quan un servidor vulgui guardar una galeta o esborrar-la del seu ordinador. Pot trobar les instruccions a la configuració de seguretat al seu navegador web.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Exemples:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;· Si utilitza Microsoft Internet Explorer, a l&#039;opció de menú Eines &amp;gt; Opcions d&#039;Internet &amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&amp;nbsp; Privadesa &amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;Configuració.&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Si utilitza Firefox, a l&#039;opció de menú Eines &amp;gt; Opcions &amp;gt; Privadesa &amp;gt; Galetes.&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Si utilitza Google Chrome, a l&#039;opció de menú Configuració &amp;gt; Privadesa&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Si utilitza Safari, a l&#039;opció de menú Preferències &amp;gt; Seguretat&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Pot fer servir la secció &#034;Ajuda&#034; que trobarà a la barra d&#039;eines de la majoria de navegadors per canviar la configuració del seu ordinador. No obstant això, algunes de les característiques dels nostres serveis online poden no funcionar o poden ser més difícils d&#039;accedir si rebutja totes les galetes.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Molts navegadors permeten activar un mode privat mitjançant el qual les galetes s&#039;esborren sempre després de la seva visita. Depenent de cada navegador, aquest mode privat pot tenir diferents noms. Més avall hi trobarà una llista dels navegadors més comuns i els diferents noms d&#039;aquest &#034;mode privat&#034;:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;· Internet Explorer 8 i superior: InPrivate&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Firefox 3.5 i superior: Navegació Privada&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Google Chrome 10 i superior: Incògnit&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Safari 2 i superior: Navegació Privada&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Opera 10.5 i superior: Navegació Privada&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Llegeixi atentament la secció d&#039;ajuda del seu navegador per tenir més informació sobre com activar el &#034;mode privat&#034;. Podrà continuar visitant la nostra web encara que el seu navegador estigui en &#034;mode privat&#034;. No obstant això, l&#039;experiència d&#039;usuari pot ser que no sigui òptima i que algunes utilitats no funcionin.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX li agraeix que activi l&#039;acceptació de galetes. Això ens ajuda a obtenir dades més precises que ens permeten millorar el contingut i el disseny de la nostra pàgina web per adaptar-lo a les seves preferències.&lt;/p&gt;</value></preference><preference><name>portletSetupShowBorders</name><value>false</value></preference><preference><name>tr_TR_htmlcode</name><value>&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong style=&#034;color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&#034;&gt;[EDITAR TEXTO POLÍTICA DE COOKIES]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h1&gt;Çerezler Politikası&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX kullanıcılara bu uyarı aracılığıyla, kullanıcı sitenin farklı sayfalarında gezinirken çerezlerin kullanılabileceğini belirtir. Web sitemizin kullanımı sırasında, gizlilik politikamıza uygun olarak çerezlerin kullanımı kabul eder ve buna izin verirsiniz.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Çerezlerin kullanım amacı sadece kullanıcıların tercihlerini hatırlamaktır (dil, ülke, oturum açma, tarayıcının özellikleri, Web sitemizin kullanım bilgileri, vs.)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Tercihlerinizi hatırlayarak kullandığınız bilgisayarın özelliklerini bilebiliriz ve böylece size daha iyi bir navegasyon deneyimi sunabiliriz. Çerezler Web sitemizin önceden ziyaretçi olan kullanıcının tarayıcısını ayırt etmesine ve kullanıcının sitede gezinirken belirlediği tercihleri kaydetmesine ve hatırlamasına, ana sayfanın kişiye özel olmasına, ziyaret edilen site kısımlarını tanımlamasına ya da &#039;&#039;alışveriş sepetinde&#039;&#039; bulunanları muhafaza etmesine yarar.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX kayıtlı olan kullanıcıları tanıma ve kendilerine daha iyi ve kişiselleştirilmiş bir hizmet sunma amacıyla çerezleri kullanabilir.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Ayrıca kullanıcının son ziyaret tarihi ve saatinin belirtildiği bilgiyi elde etmek, site içerisindeki bazı trafik parametrelerini ölçmek ve yapılan ziyaret sayısını tahmin etmek için de kullanılabilir; bu şekilde XXXXX daha etkin bir şekilde hizmetlerine odaklanabilir ve hizmetlerini uyarlayabilir.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Normalde Web siteleri Web sayfaları hakkında bir istatistik bilgisi elde etmek için çerezleri kullanırlar. Web sitemizdeki hareketlerinizi ve kullanımınızı istatistiki bilgileri için aldığımızı, kişisel amaçlı olmadığını unutmayın.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;Çerezlerin türleri ve amaçları&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Aşağıda Web sitemizde bulabileceğiniz çerezlerin bir listesi ve amaçları hakkında kısa birer açıklama bulacaksınız. Bunlardan hiçbirinin kişisel nitelikteki bilgileri içermediği konusunda sizi temin ederiz. Bazı çerezler ziyaretinizi kişiselleştirir, diğerleri tercihlerinizi hatırlar ve bazıları da sadece ziyaretçilerin istatistiklerini sunar.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;table border=&#034;1&#034; cellpadding=&#034;0&#034; cellspacing=&#034;0&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Çerezler&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bilgi (*)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Amaç&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;3&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;BİZE AİT ÇEREZLER&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Tamamen gerekli&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Oturum, kayıt, ücretsiz hizmetleri ücretli hizmetlerden ayırt etmek için veriler&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Kayıt yönetimi&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Kullanıcı tarafından talep edilen ve uygulanabilir hüküm ve koşullara uygun olan bilgileri topluma sunma hizmeti&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;3&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;ÜÇÜNCÜ ŞAHISLARA AİT ÇEREZLER&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;(alınan bilgiler aşağıda belirtilen üçüncü şahıslara sunulur)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td rowspan=&#034;7&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Analitikler&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Google Analytics&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Ziyaret sayısı, ziyaret edilen sayfa veya kısımlar, gezinme süresi, sayfaya girmeden önce ziyaret edilen siteler, kullanılan arama motoru hakkındaki detaylar.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Web sitesinin trafiği hakkındaki istatistik raporları, toplam takipçisi ve belirli bir reklam kampanyasındaki takipçi.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Comscore&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Ziyaret sayısı, ziyaret edilen sayfa veya kısımlar, gezinme süresi, sayfaya girmeden önce ziyaret edilen siteler, kullanılan arama motoru hakkındaki detaylar.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Web sitesinin trafiği hakkındaki istatistik raporları, toplam takipçisi ve belirli bir reklam kampanyasındaki takipçi.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Score Card Research (Full Circle Studies, Inc.)&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Gezinme süresi, ziyaret edilen web sitesi ve gezinme ile ilişkili bilgiler&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Web sitesine yapılan ziyaretlerin genel şablonları hakkında rapor oluşturmak.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;/tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/table&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;(*) Kullanıcının cihazı ile ilgili olan bu çerezler aracılığıyla elde edilen bilgiler, eğer sadece bu web sitesine kayıtlı iseniz kişisel bilgiler ile birleştirilebilir.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h3&gt;Koruma önlemleri&lt;/h3&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Kullanıcı, aldığı çerezleri kabul edip etmeme ya da bir sunucu çerezleri kaydetmek istediğinde tarayıcısında çerezleri alıp almaması ya da bunları bilgisayarından silmesi için gerekli yapılandırmayı yapabilir. Web tarayıcınızda güvenlik yapılandırması hakkındaki talimatları bulabilirsiniz.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Örnek:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;· Eğer Microsoft Internet Explorer kullanıyorsanız, menü seçeneğinden Araçlar &amp;gt; İnternet Seçenekleri &amp;gt; Gizlilik &amp;gt; Yapılandırma.&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Eğer Firefox kullanıyorsanız, menü seçeneğinden Araçlar &amp;gt; Seçenekleri&amp;gt; Gizlilik &amp;gt; Çerezler.&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Eğer Google Chrome kullanıyorsanız, menü seçeneği Yapılandırma &amp;gt; Gizlilik&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Eğer Safari kullanıyorsanız menü seçeneği Tercihler &amp;gt; Güvenlik&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Bilgisayarının ayarlarını değiştirmek için tarayıcıların büyük bir çoğunluğunun araçlar barında bulunan &#039;&#039;Yardım&#039;&#039; kısmını kullanabilirsiniz, fakat tüm çerezleri reddederseniz, çevrim içi hizmetlerimizin bazı özellikleri çalışmayabilir ya da erişim zorlaşabilir.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Birçok tarayıcı, ziyaret ettikten sonra çerezleri silen özel bir modu aktive etme şansı sunmaktadır. Her bir tarayıcıya göre, bu özel modun farklı isimleri olabilir, aşağıda en yaygın şekilde kullanılan tarayıcıların bir listesini ve bu &#039;&#039;özel modun&#039;&#039; farklı isimlerini bulabilirsiniz:&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;· Internet Explorer 8 ve üstü: InPrivate&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· FireFox 3.5 ve üstü: Özel Navegasyon&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Google Chrome 10 ve üstü: Incognito&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Safari 2 ve üstü: Özel Navegasyon&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· Opera 10.5 ve üstü: Özel Navegasyon&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Lütfen &#039;&#039;özel modun&#039;&#039; nasıl aktive edileceği konusunda daha fazla bilgi almak için tarayıcınızın yardım kısmını dikkatlice okuyunuz. Tarayıcınız &#039;&#039;özel modda&#039;&#039; olsa dahi Web sitemizi ziyaret edebilirsiniz, ancak kullanıcı deneyimi iyi olmayabilir ve bazı işlevler kullanılamayabilir.&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;XXXXX çerezleri kabul ettiğiniz için size teşekkür eder; bu Web sitemizin içeriğini ve tasarımını tercihlerine uyarlamak amacıyla daha da iyi bir hale getirmek adına en kesin bilgileri almamızda bize yardımcı olur.&lt;/p&gt;</value></preference><preference><name>zh_CN_htmlcode</name><value>&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong style=&#034;color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&#034;&gt;[EDITAR TEXTO POLÍTICA DE COOKIES]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;h1&gt;Cookies政策&lt;/h1&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;西班牙电信数字教育公司通过此消息通知广大用户，当用户浏览网站的不同页面时，可使用cookies。在使用我们的网站期间，根据我们的隐私政策，您明确接受并授权cookies的使用。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;Cookies的使用专门用于记录用户的偏好（语言，国家，登录，浏览器功能，我们网站的使用信息等。）&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;通过对偏好的记录，我们将了解您正在使用的计算机的特点，以便为您提供更好的浏览体验。Cookies可帮助我们的网站将用户的浏览器区分为已经进行过访问的访问者，并保存记录用户在浏览网站时进行的偏好设置，自定义主页，确定网站的哪些部分已经访问过， 或保存在“购物车”中所选产品的记录。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;西班牙电信数字教育公司能够使用cookies，识别已进行过注册的用户，提供提供更好更个性化的服务。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;也可用于获取有关用户上次访问的日期和时间信息，以测量站点内的某些流量参数并估计访问次数，以便西班牙电信数字教育公司可以更有效地提供和调整服务。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;通常网站使用cookies来获取有关网页的统计信息。请注意，我们收集有关用户网站操作和使用的数据作为统计数据，而非个人数据。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;cookies的类型和用途&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;以下是可以在我们的网站上找到的cookies列表，及其简要用途描述。我们保证，没有任何的cookies记录有关个人身份的信息。一些cookies个性化用户的访问，另一些记录使用偏好，其它cookies仅提供访问者的统计数据。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;table border=&#034;1&#034; cellpadding=&#034;0&#034; cellspacing=&#034;0&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cookies&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;信息(*)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;用途&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;3&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;自有COOKIES&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;绝对有必要&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;会话，注册，区分免费服务与支付服务的数据&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;注册管理&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;根据适用的条款和条件，提供用户所要求的信息和服务&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;3&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;第三方COOKIES&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;（以下收集的信息由第三方提供）&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td rowspan=&#034;7&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;分析&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;谷歌分析&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;访问次数，浏览页面次数或会话次数，导航时间，进入页面前所访问的网站，所用浏览器的详细信息。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;网站流量、总目标人群以及某个确定的广告活动期间的目标人群的统计报告。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;Comscore&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;访问次数，浏览页面次数或会话次数，导航时间，进入页面前所访问的网站，所用浏览器的详细信息。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;网站流量、总目标人群以及某个确定的广告活动期间的目标人群的统计报告。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td colspan=&#034;2&#034;&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;记分卡研究（Full Circle Studies公司）&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;导航时间，访问网站及与导航相关的信息&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;p&gt;创建关于网站访问一般模式的报告。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]			&lt;/td&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]		&lt;/tr&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]	&lt;/tbody&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]&lt;/table&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;(*) 通过这些cookies获取的与用户设备有关的信息，仅在用户在本网站上注册时才会与用户的个人数据相结合。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;安全防护&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;用户可将其浏览器配置为接受或不接受所接收到的cookies，以便服务器在保存cookies或从计算机中删除cookies时浏览器对其进行通知。可在Web浏览器的安全设置中找到说明。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;示例：&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;如果使用微软IE浏览器，位于菜单选项“工具”&amp;gt;“网络选项”&amp;gt;“隐私”&amp;gt;“设置”。&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]如果使用火狐浏览器，位于菜单选项“工具”&amp;gt;“选项”&amp;gt;“隐私”&amp;gt;“Cookies”。&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]·如果您使用谷歌浏览器，位于菜单选项“设置”&amp;gt;“隐私”&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]·如果您使用Safari浏览器，位于“偏好设置”&amp;gt;“安全”&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;可以使用大多数浏览器工具栏中的“帮助”更改计算机设置，然而如果拒绝所有Cookie，我们在线服务的某些功能可能无法正常工作，或难以访问。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;许多浏览器允许激活隐身模式，在访问后删除cookies。根据浏览器，此隐身模式也许有不同的名称，下面您可以找到最常见的浏览器列表以及此“隐身模式”的不同名称：&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;·IE8浏览器及更高版本：InPrivate&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]· 火狐浏览器3.5及更高版本: 私人导航&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]·谷歌浏览器10及更高版本：匿名模式&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]·Safari浏览器2及更高版本：隐身导航&lt;br /&gt;[$NEW_LINE$]·Opera浏览器10.5及更高版本：隐身导航&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;请仔细阅读浏览器的帮助部分，详细了解如何激活“隐身模式”。即使浏览器处于“隐身模式”，也可以继续访问我们的网站，但用户体验可能不是最佳的，某些应用程序可能无法使用。&lt;/p&gt;[$NEW_LINE$][$NEW_LINE$]&lt;p&gt;西班牙电信数字教育公司感谢您接受cookies的使用，这有助于我们获得更准确的数据，能够根据您的喜好改进我们网站的内容和设计。&lt;/p&gt;</value></preference></portlet-preferences>'),
